olean result for every row\n","\n","Example output:\n","\n","```python\n","False\n","False\n","True\n","False\n","True\n","...\n","```\n","\n","where:\n","\n","* False → First occurrence\n","* True → Duplicate occurrence\n","\n","### Why Is It Slow?\n","\n","Because the operation scans the entire dataset and performs duplicate checks on millions of song names.\n","\n","The larger the dataset, the longer operations such as:\n","\n","```python\n","duplicated()\n","drop_duplicates()\n","groupby()\n","merge()\n","value_counts()\n","```\n","\n","may take.\n","\n","### Faster Alternatives\n","\n","If you only want the number of duplicates:\n","\n","```python\n","info['name'].duplicated().sum()\n","```\n","\n","If you only want to know whether duplicates exist:\n","\n","```python\n","info['name'].duplicated().any()\n","```\n","\n","### Conclusion\n","\n","Nothing is wrong with the notebook.\n","\n","`info.duplicated(subset='name')` takes time because Pandas must examine and compare song names across a very large dataset containing millions of records.\n"],"metadata":{"id":"Nc0Flb2qjctK"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["info.drop_duplicates(subset='name',inplace=True)"],"metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2022-03-12T07:58:45.736551Z","iopub.execute_input":"2022-03-12T07:58:45.737291Z","iopub.status.idle":"2022-03-12T07:58:47.006014Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2022-03-12T07:58:45.737245Z","shell.execute_reply":"2022-03-12T07:58:47.004974Z"},"trusted":true,"id":"a8RxYVBCe6W5","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1780491243553,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":216,"user":{"displayName":"practice session","userId":"06899126492144380653"}}},"execution_count":17,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## 4. Exploratory Data Analysis and Data Preprocessing"],"metadata":{"id":"dwOwxQpFn0Zg"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### 4.1 Check shape"],"metadata":{"id":"rwRawVY1n25_"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["songs.shape"],"metadata":{"id":"dN5yUZein6e1","ex