aana\n","* JioSaavn\n","\n","While it is not operating at the scale of millions of users and songs, the recommendation concept is fundamentally the same.\n","\n","## Recommendation Flow\n","\n","Selected Song\n","↓\n","Similarity Engine\n","↓\n","Recommended Songs\n","\n","### Internal Processing Flow\n","\n","User Selects Song\n","↓\n","TF-IDF Feature Extraction\n","↓\n","Cosine Similarity Calculation\n","↓\n","Find Most Similar Songs\n","↓\n","Display Recommendations\n","\n","## Example\n","\n","Input Song:\n","\n","Arbolito de Navidad\n","\n","↓\n","\n","Recommendation Engine\n","\n","↓\n","\n","Recommended Songs:\n","\n","* 華麗なるロンド\n","* Angeli (Suoni Rilassanti)\n","* Let's Dance Tonight\n","* Arbolito de Navidad\n","* Unplugged Medley\n","\n","## Features Implemented\n","\n","✅ Local Model Save\n","\n","✅ Local Model Load\n","\n","✅ Default Song Input\n","\n","✅ Custom User Input\n","\n","✅ Dynamic Recommendations\n","\n","✅ Real Similarity-Based Results\n","\n","✅ Tabular Output Display\n","\n","✅ No Retraining Required\n","\n","## Deployment Workflow\n","\n","Training Notebook\n","↓\n","Build TF-IDF Features\n","↓\n","Build Cosine Similarity Matrix\n","↓\n","Save Local Model (song_model.pkl)\n","\n","---\n","\n","Inference Mode\n","\n","---\n","\n","Load song_model.pkl\n","↓\n","User Enters Song Name\n","↓\n","Find Similar Songs\n","↓\n","Display Recommendations\n","\n","## Final Conclusion\n","\n","The project now functions as a Content-Based Music Recommendation System.\n","\n","Instead of predicting a numeric value, the system recommends songs that are most similar to the selected song using TF-IDF vectorization and cosine similarity techniques.\n","\n","This is the same core recommendation concept used by modern music streaming platforms, adapted to a smaller dataset and local deployment workflow.\n"],"metadata":{"id":"6Vb1BYXYlbbr"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"3G6eva4jlFgH"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code"